数据分析过程(Data Analysis Process)
#####步骤：
- Question Phase 需要提出想要回答或解决的问题
- Wrangling Phase 数据再加工。它包括两个方面：数据采集(data acquisition)和数据整理(data cleaning)。
- Explore Phase 数据探索，需要培养直觉(build intuition)并找出数据模式(Find patterns)
- Drawing Conclusions Phase(or make predictions) 熟悉数据之后，通常需要总结或进行预测
- Communication Phase 与他人交流你的研究结果

Data acquisition([数据整理](https://cn.udacity.com/course/data-wrangling-with-mongodb--ud032))：

- Downloading files
- Accessing an API
- Scraping a web page
- Combine data from different formats

Data format
CSV(逗号分割值) - Comma Separated Values

CSV文件特点：

- Like a Spreadsheet with no formulas(类似于不含公式的电子表格)
- Easy to process with code(unlike .xlsx) 比较容易通过代码处理，这与某些文件不同，例如Microsoft Excel使用的XLSX文件 

课程3：数据分析过程，缺失的参与记录
Investigating First Problem

Why are students missing from daily_engagement?

- Identify surprising data points (Any enrollment record with no corresponding engagement data)
- Print out one or a few surprising data points

课程3：数据分析过程，检查更多问题记录
Investigating Data Problems
1.Identify surprising data points, if any
2.Print out one or a few surprising points
3.Fix any problems you find

- More investigation may be necessary
- or there might not be a problem!

 

